Poppy’s Picnic MIGHTY MINCE BEEF - made with grass fed beef... and no bone!

No weird ingredients you don’t recognise, no chemicals, flavourings, fillers or artificial additives – just raw dog food, freshly prepared and frozen for your convenience. "

" A lean, single-protein recipe that’s easy on digestion - and big on flavour.

This is a species-appropriate, high meat content dog food made with low-fat, low-purine rabbit, gently dehydrated and cold-pressed (in the UK) for convenience.

Grain Free. Naturally gentle. Perfect for dogs needing a lighter touch.

No fillers, no preservatives, no added vitamins or minerals, no artificial colours or flavours - and absolutely nothing you can’t pronounce. That’s our promise.

Cold-pressed at just 45°C to lock in nutrients that are often destroyed in traditional baked kibble.

Proudly made in the UK, using a single, novel protein source.

Ideal for dogs who thrive on a lighter, cleaner diet - whether they’re managing sensitivities, weight, or just living life a little leaner. "
